    },
    {
      "id": "1f60dc8f-a0db-81bb-90b7-f842b899f790",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "created_time": "2025-05-17T03:35:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-05-17T03:35:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "Alex"
    },
    {
      "id": "1f60dc8f-a0db-81db-8a09-dc92596977da",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "created_time": "2025-05-17T03:35:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-05-17T03:35:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "Alex's project demonstrates a solid understanding of the course material, and the data analysis he conducted is well-executed. The presentation of his findings is clear, and his use of visualizations helps support his argument. However, I felt his hypothesis could have been stated more concisely to really sharpen the focus of his paper."
    },
    {
      "id": "1f60dc8f-a0db-81dd-a200-f0a63f17d828",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "created_time": "2025-05-17T03:35:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-05-17T03:35:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "Overall, I've assigned Alex's project a grade of B+. This reflects the strengths in his work, but also the need to work on tightening up his hypothesis and research question."
    },
    {
      "id": "1f60dc8f-a0db-813c-880f-d5a93735a2fb",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "created_time": "2025-05-17T03:35:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-05-17T03:35:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "Emily"
    },
    {
      "id": "1f60dc8f-a0db-81b0-b055-e096b610697a",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "created_time": "2025-05-17T03:35:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-05-17T03:35:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "Emily's project was one of the strongest in the class. She demonstrated an excellent grasp of the theoretical concepts, and her data analysis was incredibly thorough. Her hypothesis was very clearly stated, and her argument was logically structured. I awarded Emily's project an A."
    },
    {
      "id": "1f60dc8f-a0db-818e-b81c-c085fcaf3ce6",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "created_time": "2025-05-17T03:35:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-05-17T03:35:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "James"
    },
    {
      "id": "1f60dc8f-a0db-81ab-996d-c9beeea0d4cd",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "created_time": "2025-05-17T03:35:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-05-17T03:35:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "James' project showed promise, but suffered from some gaps in the analysis and a lack of clarity in his writing. While he covered the key requirements, I felt his project could have benefited from more time spent on revising and polishing the final draft. James received a B."
    },
    {
      "id": "1f60dc8f-a0db-81ff-8ce7-c867d4e02778",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "created_time": "2025-05-17T03:35:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-05-17T03:35:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "Sarah"
    },
    {
      "id": "1f60dc8f-a0db-8152-bdba-cbd46d4e6923",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "created_time": "2025-05-17T03:35:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-05-17T03:35:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "Sarah's project was well-researched and covered all the necessary elements. However, I felt her analysis could have gone into greater depth in certain areas. Her overall argument was coherent, but lacked some of the sophistication I was hoping to see. Sarah's project received a B-."
    }
  ]

{"to":["alex@student.university.edu"],"subject":"Feedback on Your Project","body":"Hi Alex,

Thank you for the time and effort you put into your recent project. Your work shows a strong grasp of the key concepts we have been covering, and the data analysis you performed was thorough and clearly presented. The visualizations you included were particularly effective in illustrating your findings and made your argument easy to follow.

As you continue refining this project (or as you move on to future work), I encourage you to focus on sharpening the wording of your hypothesis. A concise, clearly stated research question will help guide the reader and make the overall narrative even more compelling.

If you would like to discuss any of these points in greater detail, feel free to reach out and we can set up a quick meeting.

Best regards,
[Your Name]"}
